<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Principal Dashboard</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f6f8;
      color: #333;
    }
    header {
      background-color: #1f3b58;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    .container {
      display: flex;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .sidebar {
      width: 220px;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-right: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 20px;
      height: 100vh;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
    }
    .sidebar h3 {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #888;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .sidebar a {
      display: block;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 15px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      background-color: #eef3f7;
      color: #333;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: 0.2s ease;
    }
    .sidebar a:hover {
      background-color: #dbe5ef;
    }
    .main {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 20px 40px;
    }
    .welcome {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .subtext {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .cards {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .card {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 220px;
    }
    .card h4 {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
      color: #1f3b58;
    }
    .card p {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #0077b6;
    }
    .info-section {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .info-section h3 {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #1f3b58;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .info-section p {
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #444;
    }
    .confidential {
      background-color: #fff3cd;
      border-left: 5px solid #ffc107;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .confidential h4 {
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
      color: #856404;
    }
    .confidential p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #5a4d02;
    }
    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
    table th, table td {
      padding: 10px 15px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      text-align: left;
    }
    table th {
      background-color: #ecf0f1;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .container { flex-direction: column; }
      .sidebar {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        border-right: none;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
      }
      .main { padding: 20px; }
      .cards { flex-direction: column; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    Principal Dashboard
  </header>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="sidebar">
      <h3>Navigation</h3>
      <a href="/user/teacher">View All Teachers</a>
      <a href="/user/student">View All Students</a>
    </div>

    <div class="main">
      <div class="welcome">Welcome, Principal</div>
      <div class="subtext">Hereâ€™s a summary of your school management tools.</div>

      <div class="cards">
        <div class="card">
          <h4>Total Teachers</h4>
          <p>24</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h4>Total Students</h4>
          <p>350</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="info-section">
        <h3>About Your Role</h3>
        <p>
          As the Principal, you are responsible for leading academic planning, managing faculty and students, ensuring school compliance, and maintaining the overall quality of education. 
          You can access teacher and student lists to stay updated and address any academic needs or concerns.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="confidential">
        <h4>Confidential: Internal Notices</h4>
        <p>
          Only visible to the Principal. Please review the latest staff performance evaluations and budget adjustments.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="info-section">
        <h3>Staff Evaluation Reports</h3>
        <p>Annual performance reviews for selected staff members:</p>
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Teacher Name</th>
