              <td>Pending training on new curriculum.</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="info-section">
        <h3>Finance & Budget Overview</h3>
        <p>Summary of departmental budgets for this academic year:</p>
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Department</th>
